    * Petal width: 1.1-1.8 cm
    * Sepal length: 4.9-6.9 cm
    * Sepal width: 2.7-4.3 cm
- Virginica:
    * Petal length: 6-7.5 cm
    * Petal width: 2.1-3.5 cm
    * Sepal length: 5.1-7 cm
    * Sepal width: 2.1-4 cm

## Task Evaluation
